text: Presles () is a former commune in the Calvados department in the Normandy region in northwestern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Valdallière.Arrêté préfectoral 13 October 2015 ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Calvados department ==References== Category:Former communes of Calvados (department) Category:Calvados communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia
